    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable and well-maintained ride? This car is in great shape and ready for its next adventure! It has been well-cared for, offering a smooth driving experience and a clean appearance that truly stands out. It's a solid, high-quality vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between comfort and performance.",
